      <title>泽连斯基前往土耳其寻求国防支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/zelenskiy-travels-to-turkey-in-bid-to-shore-up-defense-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽伦斯基周五将拜访土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安，埃尔多安是基辅的重要武器供应商，乌克兰寻求加强对其防御俄罗斯入侵的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/zelenskiy-travels-to-turkey-in-bid-to-shore-up-defense-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 08:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>午夜法令再次让土耳其大选似曾相识</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/midnight-decrees-hound-banks-again-in-turkish-election-deja-vu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着选举的临近和里拉的抛售，土耳其政策制定者不得不恢复旧习惯，回避利率上升的前景，转而对贷款机构进行微观管理以控制货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/midnight-decrees-hound-banks-again-in-turkish-election-deja-vu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 08:25:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前首相特雷莎·梅不会寻求连任国会议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/former-prime-minister-theresa-may-won-t-seek-re-election-as-mp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前首相特雷莎·梅不会寻求连任国会议员，她是保守党最资深的议员之一，在执政党准备迎接今年晚些时候的艰难选举之际，她将辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/former-prime-minister-theresa-may-won-t-seek-re-election-as-mp</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核监管机构要求俄罗斯结束对乌克兰工厂的占领</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nuclear-watchdog-demands-russia-end-occupation-of-ukraine-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能监管机构重申，由于担心安全状况恶化可能导致核电站崩溃，因此再次要求俄罗斯将欧洲最大核电站交还给乌克兰控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/nuclear-watchdog-demands-russia-end-occupation-of-ukraine-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:21:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>这是犯罪和犯罪香港新保安法案的处罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/here-are-the-crimes-punishments-under-hk-s-new-security-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港周五公布了一份长达 212 页的拟议新国安法法案，政府正在寻求快速立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/here-are-the-crimes-punishments-under-hk-s-new-security-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙极右翼政党希望利用抗议投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/portugal-election-2024-far-right-chega-may-capitalize-on-voter-anger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总理安东尼奥·科斯塔突然辞职后，葡萄牙将于本周末举行选举，这让选民有机会要么坚持社会党，要么选择变革并加入整个欧洲的右倾趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/portugal-election-2024-far-right-chega-may-capitalize-on-voter-anger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登国情咨文演讲的要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/key-takeaways-from-biden-s-2024-state-of-the-union-speech-to-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将自己定位为抵御民主威胁浪潮的堡垒，并将他的前任唐纳德·特朗普描绘成应对这些危险负责的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/key-takeaways-from-biden-s-2024-state-of-the-union-speech-to-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在投票前通过降低烹饪天然气价格来吸引选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-slashes-cooking-gas-prices-ahead-of-national-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 周五宣布，印度已将液化石油气钢瓶价格下调 100 卢比，以减轻家庭经济负担，努力在大选前几周吸引选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-slashes-cooking-gas-prices-ahead-of-national-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港拟在新国安法中对犯罪行为判处无期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/hk-publishes-article-23-draft-as-it-fast-tracks-new-security-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港在一份安全措施草案中提议对与叛国和叛乱有关的罪行判处无期徒刑，官员们正在寻求快速立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/hk-publishes-article-23-draft-as-it-fast-tracks-new-security-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:25:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在国情咨文中启动2024年竞选，瞄准特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/biden-speech-to-cast-trump-as-bent-on-revenge-and-retribution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图为他与唐纳德·特朗普的连任再战注入新的活力，他发表了一场激烈而尖锐的政治国情咨文演讲，与共和党人发生争执，并针对了一个他从未透露姓名的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/biden-speech-to-cast-trump-as-bent-on-revenge-and-retribution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 23:07:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
